    "en": {
      "title": "After 100 days, the protest field was cleared",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Kandy- George E.T. After 100 days, the Kota Ko Kama parade camp set up in Silva Mawatha has been removed.",
        "As the annual Perahera Utsavam of Kandy Sri Dalatha House is about to begin in the coming days, the protest site has been removed following a request by the police to remove it.",
        "Commenting on this, Timudu Abeykon, an activist of the protest field, said that this field has been removed temporarily and in the future, such a protest field will be created if the current rulers lead an anti-people regime."
      ],
